# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# __sub__ dict-presence — operator.contains(Cls.__dict__, '__sub__')
#
# All 14 asyncio classes return false for __sub__.
# No asyncio type defines subtraction.
# asyncio.Semaphore tracks an internal counter; decrementing via acquire()
#   is an async protocol, not the - operator.
# asyncio.TaskGroup manages a dynamic set of tasks via create_task(), but
#   does not define set-difference semantics via -.
# asyncio.BoundedSemaphore adds a bounded check over Semaphore; no arithmetic.
# asyncio.Queue, Handle, TimerHandle, Lock, Condition: no subtraction defined.
# asyncio.Timeout/StreamReader/StreamWriter: async utility objects; no -.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

