# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# __mul__ dict-presence — operator.contains(Cls.__dict__, '__mul__')
#
# All 14 asyncio classes return false for __mul__.
# No asyncio type defines multiplication or repetition.
# asyncio.Queue does not support queue * n for replication of queues.
# asyncio.Semaphore/Lock/Condition/BoundedSemaphore: resource guards with
#   no sequence-repetition or numeric-multiplication semantics.
# asyncio.Handle/TimerHandle: callback handles; repetition is undefined.
# asyncio.Timeout: an async deadline context manager; no * operator.
# asyncio.TaskGroup: creates tasks via create_task(); no task replication via *.
# asyncio.StreamReader/StreamWriter: byte-stream I/O objects; no repetition.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

